c51e195", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 0, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "8869de50-c7ca-4684-ba51-a994f2ef8179": {"__data__": {"id_": "8869de50-c7ca-4684-ba51-a994f2ef8179", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "/Users/darshanbalaji/Documents/healthcare-claims-ai/healthcare-claims-ai/notebooks/../data/knowledge_base/cpt_categories.txt", "file_name": "cpt_categories.txt", "file_type": "text/plain", "file_size": 1199, "creation_date": "2026-06-05", "last_modified_date": "2026-06-05"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "b2a8920c-fc39-4722-8c3b-3c5eb2e8da10", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "/Users/darshanbalaji/Documents/healthcare-claims-ai/healthcare-claims-ai/notebooks/../data/knowledge_base/cpt_categories.txt", "file_name": "cpt_categories.txt", "file_type": "text/plain", "file_size": 1199, "creation_date": "2026-06-05", "last_modified_date": "2026-06-05"}, "hash": "d0efee14ec1399314782ca2f79a3d2ccadd6e5afb6d2612f0b60f490a0527862", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "CPT Code Range 99202-99215: Office or other outpatient visits (Evaluation and Management)\n  99202-99205: New patient office visits\n  99211-99215: Established patient office visits\n  99213: Most common office visit code - established patient, moderate complexity\n  99214: Established patient, moderate-high complexity\n\nCPT Code Range 93000-93799: Cardiology procedures\n  93000: Electrocardiogram (ECG/EKG)\n  93306: Echocardiography\n  93454: Cardiac catheterization\n\nCPT Code Range 80000-89999: Laboratory and pathology\n  80053: Comprehensive metabolic panel\n  85025: Complete blood count (CBC)\n  83036: Hemoglobin A1c (diabetes monitoring)\n\nCPT Code Range 70000-79999: Radiology\n  71046: Chest X-ray, 2 views\n  72148: MRI lumbar spine\n  70553: MRI brain with contrast\n\nCPT Code Range 27000-29999: Orthopedic surgery (Musculoskeletal)\n  27447: Total knee replacement\n  27130: Total hip replacement\n  29881: Knee arthroscopy\n\nCPT Code Range 90000-90899: Psychiatry and behavioral health\n  90834: Psychotherapy, 45 minutes\n  90837: Psychotherapy, 60 minutes\n  90847: Family psychotherapy\n\nCPT Code Range 94000-94799: Pulmonary procedures\n  94010: Spirometry (breathing test)\n  94640: Nebulizer treatment", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 1199, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "1a9ee047-a7ff-42a8-af5f-316b3fa340be": {"__data__": {"id_": "1a9ee047-a7ff-42a8-af5f-316b3fa340be", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "/Users/darshanbalaji/Documents/healthcare-claims-ai/healthcare-claims-ai/notebooks/../data/knowledge_base/denial_reasons.txt", "file_name": "denial_reasons.txt", "file_type": "text/plain", "file_size": 1032, "creation_date": "2026-06-05", "last_modified_date": "2026-06-05"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "a3eb404b-9ea2-4c59-b7f9-41449d50de23", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "/Users/darshanbalaji/Documents/healthcare-claims-ai/healthcare-claims-ai/notebooks/../data/knowledge_base/denial_reasons.txt", "file_name": "denial_reasons.txt", "file_type": "text/plain", "file_size": 1032, "creation_date": "2026-06-05", "last_modified_date": "2026-06-05"}, "hash": "972e44f6196e02992817e9f312e4313b753c1e3053bab4ea57f9c289cd72386b", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "CARC Code 4: The service/equipment/drug is not covered by the plan.\nCARC Code 16: Claim/service lacks information or has submission/billing error.\nCARC Code 29: The time limit for filing has expired.\nCARC Code 50: These are non-covered services because this is not deemed a medical necessity.\nCARC Code 97: The benefit for this service is included in the payment/allowance for another service.\nCARC Code 151: Payment adjusted because the payer deems the information submitted does not support this many/frequency of services.\nCARC Code 167: This (these) diagnosis(es) is (are) not covered.\nCARC Code 197: Precertification/authorization/notification/pre-treatment absent.\n\nCommon denial patterns:\nMedical necessity denial: ICD and CPT codes are clinically inconsistent.\nDuplicate claim denial: same patient, provider, CPT, and date submitted more than once.\nTimely filing denial: claim submitted after the payer deadlines (typically 90-365 days).\nPrior authorization denial: procedure required advance approval that was not obtained.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 1032, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "30c4bb9d-943f-47d1-bf75-25d7f8362ce7": {"__data__": {"id_": "30c4bb9d-943f-47d1-bf75-25d7f8362ce7", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "/Users/darshanbalaji/Documents/healthcare-claims-ai/healthcare-claims-ai/notebooks/../data/knowledge_base/icd_chapters.txt", "file_name": "icd_chapters.txt", "file_type": "text/plain", "file_size": 887, "creation_date": "2026-06-05", "last_modified_date": "2026-06-05"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "eb7c3ada-9d6d-4055-9443-f24b052a7e39", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "/Users/darshanbalaji/Documents/healthcare-claims-ai/healthcare-claims-ai/notebooks/../data/knowledge_base/icd_chapters.txt", "file_name": "icd_chapters.txt", "file_type": "text/plain", "file_size": 887, "creation_date": "2026-06-05", "last_modified_date": "2026-06-05"}, "hash": "0d5f098d97cd7bf992de1d461c8fdbd3f516413a551b23eb18fe390a8530bdba", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "ICD-10 Chapter I: Certain infectious and parasitic diseases (A00-B99)\nICD-10 Chapter II: Neoplasms - cancers and tumors (C00-D49)\nICD-10 Chapter III: Diseases of blood and immune system (D50-D89)\nICD-10 Chapter IV: Endocrine, nutritional and metabolic diseases (E00-E89)\n  Includes: diabetes (E11), obesity (E66), thyroid disorders (E00-E07)\nICD-10 Chapter V: Mental, behavioral and neurodevelopmental disorders (F01-F99)\n  Includes: depression (F32), anxiety (F41), substance use (F10-F19)\nICD-10 Chapter IX: Diseases of the circulatory system (I00-I99)\n  Includes: heart attack (I21), heart failure (I50), hypertension (I10)\nICD-10 Chapter X: Diseases of the respiratory system (J00-J99)\n  Includes: pneumonia (J18), COPD (J44), asthma (J45)\nICD-10 Chapter XIII: Diseases of musculoskeletal system (M00-M99)\n  Includes: osteoarthritis (M17), back pain (M54), rheumatoid arthritis (M05)", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 887, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}}}